==Spanish==

===Pronunciation===
{{IPA|/on/}}

===Suffix===
'''-ón''' {{m}} '''-ona''' {{f}}

# emphasizes that something is large, grand, intense, important
# emphasizes contempt for subject
# suffixed to verbs, doing something repeatedly or often
#: ''[[llorón]]'' - something or someone that cries (from ''[[llorar]]'')
#: ''[[mirón]]'' - something or someone that watches (from ''[[mirar]]'')
# indicates a lack of something
#: ''[[pelón]]'' - with little hair (from ''[[pelo]]'')

===Usage notes===
The suffix produces adjectives or nouns.

